---
---
    <header class="hero" id="top">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span class="mark">AGYL</span>
          <span class="div">/</span>
          <span>The operating layer for AI-ready data</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="hero-title">Your AI is only as smart as <em>the records</em> it reads from.<br>AGYL is the <em>operating layer</em> that makes them <em>AI-ready</em>.</h1>

        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <p>No AI agent, copilot, or company brain can reason on records that disagree with each other. <b>AGYL is the layer that makes them agree.</b> It reads across your systems, decides what is true about every record that matters, and hands clean, governed records to whatever reads them next.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta-row">
              <a href="#close" class="btn btn-primary">See it on your data <span class="arr">→</span></a>
              <a href="#what-you-get" class="btn btn-ghost">How AGYL works</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-vis">
            <div class="vh">
              <span>RESOLUTION · LIVE FEED</span>
              <span class="live">RUNNING</span>
            </div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 540 475" role="img" aria-label="A record resolving live inside the operating layer">
              <defs>
                <style>
                  .hp-cap{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.16em;fill:rgba(245,244,241,.5);text-transform:uppercase}
                  .hp-cap-ink{fill:#F5F4F1}
                  .hp-h{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;fill:#F5F4F1;letter-spacing:-.005em}
                  .hp-lbl{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;fill:#F5F4F1;letter-spacing:.02em}
                  .hp-mute{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:400;fill:rgba(245,244,241,.5);letter-spacing:.02em}
                  .hp-mute-ink{fill:rgba(245,244,241,.78)}
                  .hp-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:300;fill:#F5F4F1;letter-spacing:-.025em}
                  .hp-warn{fill:#C9A875}
                  .hp-good{fill:#7A9A7F}
                  .hp-bar{transform-origin:left center;animation:hpBar 2.4s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1) backwards;}
                  @keyframes hpBar{from{transform:scaleX(0);} to{transform:scaleX(1);}}
                  .hp-rfade{animation:hpFade 1s ease-out backwards;}
                  @keyframes hpFade{from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(4px);} to{opacity:1;}}
                  .hp-cursor{animation:hpBlink 1.2s steps(1) infinite;}
                  @keyframes hpBlink{50%{opacity:0;}}
                  .hp-stream{stroke-dasharray:4 6;animation:hpStream 2.2s linear infinite;}
                  @keyframes hpStream{to{stroke-dashoffset:-60;}}
                </style>
              </defs>

              <text class="hp-cap" x="0" y="14">3 SOURCES RECONCILED · UPDATED 2s AGO</text>

              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:0s">
                <rect x="0" y="22" width="540" height="50" fill="rgba(201,168,117,.08)" stroke="rgba(201,168,117,.32)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-warn" x="14" y="42">SALESFORCE · CRM</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="14" y="60">Halsey, Inc.</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="42" text-anchor="end">ARR $48,000</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="60" text-anchor="end">last edit: Mar 4</text>
              </g>

              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:.3s">
                <rect x="0" y="80" width="540" height="50" fill="rgba(201,168,117,.08)" stroke="rgba(201,168,117,.32)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-warn" x="14" y="100">SLACK · #revenue-ops thread</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="14" y="118">"Halsey just confirmed $52.4K Q1 invoice"</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="100" text-anchor="end">m.chen · 2d ago</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="118" text-anchor="end">attachment: invoice.pdf</text>
              </g>

              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:.6s">
                <rect x="0" y="138" width="540" height="50" fill="rgba(201,168,117,.08)" stroke="rgba(201,168,117,.32)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-warn" x="14" y="158">NOTION · Account brief, Halsey</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="14" y="176">Halsey Industrial Supply</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="158" text-anchor="end">renewal: "April"</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="176" text-anchor="end">owner: J. Morales</text>
              </g>

              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:.95s">
                <line x1="270" y1="198" x2="270" y2="226" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.5)" stroke-width="1" class="hp-stream"/>
                <path d="M264 222 L270 230 L276 222" fill="none" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.5)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-cap-ink" x="270" y="214" text-anchor="middle">RESOLVING</text>
              </g>

              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:1.2s">
                <rect x="0" y="240" width="540" height="190" fill="rgba(122,154,127,.10)" stroke="rgba(122,154,127,.55)" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-good" x="14" y="262">RESOLVED RECORD · CUSTOMER MASTER</text>
                <text class="hp-cap" x="526" y="262" text-anchor="end">CONFIDENCE 0.96</text>
                <line x1="14" y1="272" x2="526" y2="272" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.10)"/>
                <text class="hp-h" x="14" y="296">Halsey, Inc.</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="14" y="314">d/b/a Halsey Industrial Supply · 7-yr customer</text>
                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="14" y="344">True ARR</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="180" y="344">$52,400</text>
                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="14" y="364">Active contract</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="180" y="364">MSA-2024-118</text>
                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="14" y="384">Renewal</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl hp-warn" x="180" y="384">Apr 14 · 47d</text>
                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="290" y="344">Owner</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="396" y="344">J. Morales</text>
                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="290" y="364">MFN clause</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="396" y="364">Yes · ¶ 7.2</text>
                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="290" y="384">Linked records</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="396" y="384">4 SKUs · 1 asset</text>
                <line x1="14" y1="402" x2="526" y2="402" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.10)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-good" x="14" y="420">DEPLOYED · CRM + SALES + RENEWAL CALENDAR</text>
              </g>

              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:1.6s">
                <text class="hp-cap" x="0" y="448">EVIDENCE CHAIN</text>
                <text class="hp-cap" x="540" y="448" text-anchor="end">5 OF 5 CITED · 1 APPROVAL APPLIED</text>
                <rect x="0" y="458" width="540" height="2" fill="rgba(245,244,241,.10)"/>
                <rect x="0" y="458" width="540" height="2" fill="#F5F4F1" class="hp-bar-loop"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-foot">
          <div>What it is<b>AI infrastructure</b></div>
          <div>Specifically<b>The operating layer above the model</b></div>
          <div>What it does<b>Makes your records AI-ready</b></div>
          <div>Who owns it<b>You do, by architecture</b></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>